t": "Because I hated him. Like so many others here, I hated his pretentiousness and his bloodthirstiness for war and death. I hated his political corruption,  and I hated how he listened to people with power over his own constituents' needs.\r\n\r\nAnd THAT is precisely why I will lay down all of that hatred in Church today, and pray for his repose. Does that mean Ive forgiven him for what he's done and what he's stood for in his life? Hardly. But, it would be wrong, and hypocritical of me as a Christian, to not wish for mercy on a fellow child of God. Even if I dont think he deserves it, it is the right thing to do.", "author": "heightnoise", "created": 1783862453279, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Test_user21", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Today in Church, I will be praying for the repose of the soul of Lindsey Graham, for one specific reason:", "last_comment_created": 1783899552420, "content": "<p>Because I hated him. Like so many others here, I hated his pretentiousness and his bloodthirstiness for war and death. I hated his political corruption,  and I hated how he listened to people with power over his own constituents' needs.</p>\n<p>And THAT is precisely why I will lay down all of that hatred in Church today, and pray for his repose. Does that mean Ive forgiven him for what he's done and what he's stood for in his life? Hardly. But, it would be wrong, and hypocritical of me as a Christian, to not wish for mercy on a fellow child of God. Even if I dont think he deserves it, it is the right thing to do.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 21